data.description: Walk-out rambler - tastefully renovated in 2012-2013 with 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, the open-concept kitchen/living/dining is great for family time and entertaining with a huge center island, ample counter and storage space, stainless steel appliances.  The living room has vaulted ceilings, fireplace, and wood burning fireplace.  There are 3 bedrooms on the main level with a large bedroom in the lower level.  The generous size owner's suite has a 3/4 bath.  Don't miss the cedar closet.  The large open lower walk out level is great for movie/game night.  The home sits on an expansive flat yard with an irrigation system and no direct back yard neighbors.  New maintenance free, vinyl siding installed August 2023.  This home is close to excellent schools, walking trails, and parks.  You will also have easy access to all the important things in life, like shopping, restaurants, and The Shops at West End are just a short drive away.
